project_descr: FORTALECIMIENTO Y CONSTRUCCIÓN DE POLITICAS CULTURALES EQUITATIVAS Y DIVERSAS EN EL DISTRITO FEDERAL.

outputs.output_descr: Contribute the institutionalization process of cultural public policies in Mexico City through applied research and systematization of experiences of citizenship building and social participation. The project will define a baseline in this subject and will provide inputs to strengthen cultural policies.

project_title: fortal. y constr. politicas culturales equitativas d.f.
